    "causal_summary": "Hallmark is a shipped design skill for AI coding assistants (\"refuses to look AI-generated\") whose four verbs — build, `audit`, `redesign`, `study` (design DNA → portable `design.md`) — plus ~29 reference docs (slop-test with 57 gates, anti-patterns, macrostructures, motion, microinteractions, color, typography, component-cookbook, design-md, study, export-formats, …) overlap heavily with sk-design's five modes (interface, foundations, motion, audit, md-generator/design-reference) and its styles database",
